    <h1>Do Immigrants Cost More Than They Contribute?<br><em>Results Vary Widely by Country</em></h1>
    <p class="theme-hero__sub">Denmark −DKK 16bn/yr, Germany −€2.1bn/yr, Sweden +SEK 6bn/yr (labour migrants only). The outcome depends heavily on migrant profile and methodology.</p>
    <div class="theme-hero__meta">
      <span class="lang-pill"><a href="/faq/fiscal-cost/">🌐 日本語</a></span>
      <span class="meta-note">Primary official sources only</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2>Country-level official data (primary sources)</h2>
